freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: My arm started to hurt again in the last couple days it might be a little to the left of the spot where the shot was but it was annoying. About 6 or 7 out of 10

freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: I forgot to report the huge fatigue yesterday which began exactly 1 hour after I experienced the bad pain in the arm that received the shot. I was so tired I just had to go to bed. I was shocked to see that it was only 7:30 PM lol ... I realized it was exactly one hour after I started to experience the pain in my arm which began exactly eight hours after the vaccination...Hmmm

Only my arm started hurting a lot yesterday 6:30 p.m. 8 hours after the shot and I couldn't lift it without severe pain . it got worse at night and then by the morning was starting to get better. it is gone now but it is worth mentioning because it was pretty bad. I did not take anything for it because I thought that I shouldn't.
